{"tid":500261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係時候利用自已手上既力量","createTime":"2017-12-15T15:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T02:25:05.000Z","uid":114483,"like":41,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1f9b058997b8dc91f7716dd274aac570ee715320","tid":500261,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:19:00.000Z","msg":"去到今日，再一次證明香港唔可以倚靠飯民呢埋賤種死政棍，唔好同我講咩大局為重，集票抗衡建制先，依家個問題就係廿年黎，飯民都只係一堆政棍，即使日後要分票大局為重需要先滿足自決派。<br />\n唔好講咩自決派都可能係政棍，至少，我睇唔到飯民有咩希望。<br />\n唔好再講咩要番工，不了，中共就係睇中你班傻閪呢點，等最後一部分人都政治冷感，香港就徹底收皮<br />\n善用你既力量，小至fb ig 大至專頁admin，善用社交媒體比全香港網民知，飯民左膠有幾垃圾，唔好一句就話要暴力抗爭，你自決派連相對既民意基礎未有，憑咩武力抗爭？<br />\n香港只有一個，好快佢會變成中國香港市<br />\n<br />\n記住一樣野，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">維持自已信念，唔好輕易比五毛引導</span>"},{"pid":"42539dc9d6842682befe36ed674fffbe8f86d99a","tid":500261,"uid":26156,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:20:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"785138da68fab79ddfa529c88aee5f2103e93f5e","tid":500261,"uid":114483,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:23:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放棄了</blockquote><br />\n我唔想放棄香港，呢到係我最愛既地方，我唔甘心咩都無做佢就要滅去，我唔想將來同我個仔講香港是我家，佢問我香港係邊，我唔想放棄"},{"pid":"c6629b7d1e05a312f69620c0a5d306a82be5ea4e","tid":500261,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T15:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09515ba7cf6438a49915a7f26fa8f54aff27adaf","tid":500261,"uid":37722,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:03:57.000Z","msg":"今次立法會少人討論得好誇張, 根本好多人都打算肉隨針板上就算, 我信好多人都有睇, 不過就無哂心機<br />\n而家呢個現況發展落去就係個個都開始愈黎愈冷感, 之後23條黎又個個都話抵死啦泛民, 直接香港玩完仲好, 再之後有第一單以言入罪又話, 香港人自己自作業, 我都否認唔到個事實, 但係呢D就真係退化返去做鍵盤戰士, 就算十年後再有革命佢地都係話有雨革都做過啦, 有用咩<br />\n雖然老實講, 我地可能真係無咩做到, 但最起碼清楚下自己既政治立場係咩, 底線又係咩, 而家好多人心入面既底線日日都比個仆街政府踩緊, 遊行示威無用, 但係咩都唔做日日比人侮辱又好好多咩? 就算無能力都好, 改變下身邊D人既睇法, 散播一下民主, 港獨思想已經比等死好<br />\n我到而家都唔認同焦土派散播失敗主義, 個D咩等比中國接管香港人等死既講法, 老實講呢種事不關己既講法係無撚聊, 同班港豬大同小異, 講就講到唔關自己事, 燒到埋身又走唔到就開始亂吠嘆氣, 根本成個過程都係自取其辱"},{"pid":"f8bed5e8f8a4432631c1f62e6316bc3ad24ea51f","tid":500261,"uid":76038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178634c5ea69b336585f0975a62d12e4d06a74e9","tid":500261,"uid":44105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:10:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209284ddc165756fecb6cb517909da02a1fedf46","tid":500261,"uid":59283,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:12:28.000Z","msg":"自決派咪泛民b隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeca36ef8e2b22aede28c1245994778d908c071b","tid":500261,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:13:05.000Z","msg":"問題係無人出黎取代泛民。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0a96a6d15d958991f18613c587dbeef1d44651","tid":500261,"uid":97814,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:14:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74f9e642a3fd2f6e9fa5c5fceb03b0f08e445622","tid":500261,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自決派咪泛民b隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔完全係"},{"pid":"e6bad053df61973be2d8d16963aa0659cfe07936","tid":500261,"uid":884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:18:57.000Z","msg":"我地做到啲咩丫講真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你真係覺得有可能實現？"},{"pid":"c8b1bd246885f8aafe9b1df2a2330e4936a1e258","tid":500261,"uid":63669,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:19:58.000Z","msg":"鍵國勇士又係到講埋啲空泛無用既廢話"},{"pid":"4669abd9f1a3c63498a089d62cadc43e91b1a55f","tid":500261,"uid":114483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:33:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我地做到啲咩丫講真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你真係覺得有可能實現？</blockquote><br />\n中共就係食正你呢啲位，你先會任佢魚肉，依家個目標先唔好放到去建國，起碼都要保住五十年不變呢樣野，唔好提早比人收返，香港人有返自治權，我地先有機會反抗"},{"pid":"fac16b0d1e86aa66501bd6283910b4184dc98833","tid":500261,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:34:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"705ea528bb96ba459ae71875b9c8bef2ebb5c9c3","tid":500261,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:35:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自決派咪泛民b隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起碼自決派係新生力，我寧願信一次佢地，好過信泛民死政棍，當然獨派亦都要得到支持，但係獨派好大機會參選都過唔到，就會用自決派自我標榜"},{"pid":"3f174682aae5d1d18093963bfd0199490c65cc8a","tid":500261,"uid":52946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:35:30.000Z","msg":"有5毛保皇唔搞 搞其他就一定戇鳩 不快d攬炒仲好"},{"pid":"4dddbc3f45426cd7bc349bed6e082249370c4d2f","tid":500261,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:37:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記得捐款！</span></span></blockquote><br />\n錢都係好重要既一環，普通平民捐錢未必有好大作用，要靠富商，無論人際關係定錢，都需要佢地。而我地要做既，就係利用我地既力量，改變整個社會風氣，令富商有動機支持自決，甚至獨立"},{"pid":"a898599b3a10127b9fb1f14a79d340d680e7d53c","tid":500261,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:38:55.000Z","msg":"鍵國派有咩做到？"},{"pid":"3fa744e0967b74e06e7451ba6b7dddeafe1c8064","tid":500261,"uid":14482,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:42:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a22aee17b38436d71461449f3194ae79c162946d","tid":500261,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed89ad8b9ed9990fad5e4fdac04fb80b06c4204","tid":500261,"uid":114483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:43:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鍵國派有咩做到？</blockquote><br />\n咩都做唔到就係因為個個好似你咁既思想，未開始做就質疑，魚蛋革命個次唔夠？打完，成個社會又要屌示威者，而你呢班廢柴就一句聲都唔出，唔幫下口，淨係匿埋係X 登到話咩大快人心，出到去又唔敢出聲，成個風氣就變做沉默左膠，咁樣落去，唔好話自決獨立，十年命你都無"},{"pid":"e601a1741a7769d64539df98952e74f161156a04","tid":500261,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:45:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解共產黨越玩越有,人哋當年成班農民可以起義<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地就要做鍵盤戰士, 其實好簡單係因為你哋廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就好簡單一早明白u can&rsquo;t beat them , join them 既道理 ， 你哋慢慢喺度浪費時間啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n躝啦死五毛<br />\n我死都唔會做中國人。<br />\n由頭到尾，我只得一個身份"},{"pid":"c3179167e3d262c0da5b8d0bd5d6c5d5d93aa1e0","tid":500261,"uid":119450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:46:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鍵國派有咩做到？</blockquote><br />\n咩都做唔到就係因為個個好似你咁既思想，未開始做就質疑，魚蛋革命個次唔夠？打完，成個社會又要屌示威者，而你呢班廢柴就一句聲都唔出，唔幫下口，淨係匿埋係X 登到話咩大快人心，出到去又唔敢出聲，成個風氣就變做沉默左膠，咁樣落去，唔好話自決獨立，十年命你都無</blockquote><br />\n你估網上依家冇屌鳩泛民言論咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n網上講完咪一樣冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aabe5c4b5ee04e88273066e8fca6bf0f0fad89d","tid":500261,"uid":14482,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:46:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73dd2a15fae8e7df3bbc765672da27c51877a2bb","tid":500261,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:46:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be50f00ee82abfe1944f297b66c43b82f4b660fe","tid":500261,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:49:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鍵國派有咩做到？</blockquote><br />\n咩都做唔到就係因為個個好似你咁既思想，未開始做就質疑，魚蛋革命個次唔夠？打完，成個社會又要屌示威者，而你呢班廢柴就一句聲都唔出，唔幫下口，淨係匿埋係X 登到話咩大快人心，出到去又唔敢出聲，成個風氣就變做沉默左膠，咁樣落去，唔好話自決獨立，十年命你都無</blockquote><br />\n你估網上依家冇屌鳩泛民言論咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n網上講完咪一樣冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有，根本得一兩成言論，仲要主流都係X 登，出面世界仲係馬照跑舞照跳，我地就係要改變呢種風氣，善用自已社交媒體既力量，政治言論一個人講就無力，一萬個人講就成為風氣，起碼要將傳統飯民既票導向自決獨派，而唔係繼續比政棍利用"},{"pid":"cb62913e9579f4d7845c3ea0a37e6c3da2a9b93b","tid":500261,"uid":14482,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:49:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c92dde4fd9e637b5bc7b008deb15c8fa4e11d344","tid":500261,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:50:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解共產黨越玩越有,人哋當年成班農民可以起義<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地就要做鍵盤戰士, 其實好簡單係因為你哋廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就好簡單一早明白u can&rsquo;t beat them , join them 既道理 ， 你哋慢慢喺度浪費時間啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n躝啦死五毛<br />\n我死都唔會做中國人。<br />\n由頭到尾，我只得一個身份</blockquote><br />\n你咪唔好做囉<br />\n<br />\n物競天擇,弱肉強食<br />\n你慢慢係自己嘅幻想世界度鍵國啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n躝啦柒頭，咁唔鍾意，留係到做乜撚？"},{"pid":"3c02303217989951e016036954e6770c2567ba01","tid":500261,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T00:50:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我就好簡單一早明白u can&rsquo;t beat them , join them 既道理 ， 你哋慢慢喺度浪費時間啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁唔一定既，地球咁大，你玩得哂咩？<br />\n我就唔住全地球都無容身之所！</blockquote><br />\n成日話香港死，我究竟想問下可以點死 ?<br />\n就算香港變到另一個上海，北京大把都唔care<br />\n<br />\n生活唔到人咩？大把鬼佬衝去住啦<br />\n<br />\n香港變內地第中一個城市已經係事實<br />\n<br />\n好心你地面對下現實，香港從來都唔係家唔家<br />\n<br />\n香港咁多年來只係一個搵錢地，怪就怪在你生活係個搵錢地都搵唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm